<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Kallesin</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-01 22:40:28</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Disease Cloud is level 9 for SKs, it cant even be scribed before level 9, and this spell comes in handy if you fear-kite a lot. before level 22, I would cast clinging darkness, disease cloud, and fear while my pet and I hit the thing in the back..I usually killed crocs/caimen in oasis till level 19.  You can use the same stratagy in EK with gorge hounds, but there is a greater risk of getting another hound or a dark stalker or a Griff on you, not to mention the risk of running into Sir Morgan (guard in EK thats KOS to DEs, trolls, and ogres, and not sure about human SKs) or another guard. Gorge hounds can be meleed at level 19 without a lot of trouble anyway. <BR>
<BR>
-my post about disease cloud and some advice to SKs<BR>
P.S. agility is good :)</font></td></tr></table>
